ight now?

=E2=80=9CNo taxes on
tips=E2=80=9D was a very smart thing the Trump campaign did to try to peel =
away the culinary workers from their union leadership, and we=E2=80=99ll se=
e how that works. But the real reason for this is because of the rural vote=
=2E Nevada has 17 counties; two of=
 them are urban=E2=80=94Reno and Vegas=E2=
=80=94and then the rest are very deep red, and they have turned out disprop=
ortionately so far in the early going. That=E2=80=99s the reason the Republ=
icans have a lead=E2=80=94it=E2=80=99s almost all because there=E2=80=99s t=
