he-vote operation looking in Nevada?

The bottom line is that the Republican Party has been historically terrible=
 here. They=E2=80=99ve been run by incompetence. They wouldn=E2=80=99t even=
 know what the word =E2=80=9Cinfrastructure=E2=80=9D or G.O.T.V. means. Rem=
